OL,3,CFormer detective who stalked ex given
OL,4,Csuspended prison sentence
OL,6,FSue Thorpe, 44, a former officer with
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police, bombarded surfing
OL,8,Finstructor Barry Henderson with
OL,9,Fabusive voicemails, texts and emails
OL,10,Fin a year-long harassment campaign
OL,11,Fafter he ended their relationship.
OL,13,FShe also used the police national
OL,14,Fcomputer to illegally look up
OL,15,Finformation about Mr Henderson
OL,16,Ffollowing the split.
