OL,3,CFormer detective who stalked ex given
OL,4,Csuspended prison sentence
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Thorpe, of Whitley Bay,
OL,7,FNorth Tyneside, was sentenced to two
OL,8,Fyears in prison, suspended for two
OL,9,Fyears after being found guilty of
OL,10,Fstalking and misuse of computer data.
OL,12,FShe was also ordered to carry out 120
OL,13,Fhours of unpaid work, 20
OL,14,Frehabilitation activity days and
OL,15,Fhanded a 10-year restraining order
OL,16,Fbanning her from any contact with Mr
OL,17,FHenderson.
