OL,3,CFormer detective who stalked ex given
OL,4,Csuspended prison sentence
OL,6,FNewcastle Crown Court heard that
OL,7,Fbetween June 2020 and September 2021,
OL,8,FThorpe sent Mr Henderson messages
OL,9,Faccusing him of being violent towards
OL,10,Fher during their five-year-long
OL,11,Frelationship and posted "untrue and
OL,12,Fseriously alarming" allegations about
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,FA judge was told she repeated these
OL,16,Fclaims to his friends, family members
OL,17,Fand new partner, and tried to harm his
OL,18,Fsurfing business by posting them on
OL,19,FFacebook and to a charity his business
OL,20,Fworked with.
