OL,3,CFormer detective who stalked ex given
OL,4,Csuspended prison sentence
OL,6,FThorpe set up a fake email address to
OL,7,Fcontact other organisations with her
OL,8,Faccusations, at one point pretending
OL,9,Fto be a concerned parent, and turned
OL,10,Fup at his workplace twice, it was said.
OL,12,FIn a victim impact statement read in
OL,13,Fcourt, Mr Henderson said Thorpe was
OL,14,F"on a mission to destroy him" and her
OL,15,Fclaims made him feel "physically sick"
OL,16,Fwhen he read them.
OL,18,FThe statement read: "Sue is clearly
OL,19,Ftrying to ruin my life and make my day
OL,20,Fto day living a nightmare.
