OL,6,F"It is embarrassing and humiliating
OL,7,Fhaving to explain to family and
OL,8,Ffriends what is happening.
OL,10,F"What Sue has done has created a
OL,11,Fmassive strain on my personal life."
OL,13,FJudge Amanda Rippon said Thorpe, who
OL,14,Fhad been a police officer for 19
OL,15,Fyears, had suffered a miscarriage of
OL,16,Ftwins following IVF and the offending
OL,17,Fhappened "at a time of her life when
OL,18,Fshe was in crisis and ill".
