OL,6,FAfter the trial in April, Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice said Thorpe had been suspended
OL,8,Ffrom the force.
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent Donna Rose,
OL,11,Fhead of Northumbria Police's
OL,12,FProfessional Standards Department,
OL,13,Fsaid: "When concerns were raised in
OL,14,Frelation to this individual, we began
OL,15,Fan investigation and they were
OL,16,Fsubsequently suspended from duty.
OL,18,F"A file was submitted to the Crown
OL,19,FProsecution Service which resulted in
OL,20,Fher being charged.
